Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: pydorita
Version: 0.1
Summary: Python client for controlling a iRobot Roomba 980 (via rest980)
Home-page: https://github.com/pschmitt/pydorita
Author: Philipp Schmitt
Author-email: philipp@schmitt.co
License: GPL3
Description: pydorita
        ============
        
        This library provides Python bindings for the iRobot Roomba 980 REST gateway
        from https://github.com/koalazak/rest980
        
        Example
        --------------
        .. code:: python
        
            from pydorita import PyDoritaClient
            # Connect to the REST980 gateway
            pd = PyDoritaClient(
                hostname='rest980-gw.lan',
                port=3000,
                username='roomba',
                password='R0mB!'
            )
            # Get the current state (ie. "run", "stuck" etc.)
            pd.phase
            # Get the current error code
            pd.error
            # Get the current battery percentage
            pd.battery
            # Get the current position
            pd.position
            # Start cleaning
            pd.clean()
            # Stop and dock
            pd.stop_and_dock()
        
Platform: UNKNOWN
